title: The Key (Wicked Pictures) 2015 Web-DL (Split-Scenes)
description:
Cast: Gigi Allens, Olivia Austin, Morgan Lee, Mercedes Carrera, Chanel Preston, Derrick Pierce, Eric Masterson, Steven St. Croix, Brad Armstrong

Unlock your desire. Four women are given the opportunity to unlock their passion and sexuality. Sexy Gigi Allens offers her friends (Olivia Austin, Mercedes Carrera, Morgan Lee, and Chanel Preston) a key to the ultimate getaway. It's here that they explore and unleash their innermost carnal desires. The result? A heart-stopping, sheet-clenching, sexual inferno!
